Private variables can be accessed from outside the class by using get and set method 

get is used to call the variable value
set is used to set the value of the variable

Syntax -

  get - start with 'get' followed by the name of the variable, with the first letter in upper case
  set - start with 'set' followed by the name of the variable, with the first letter in upper case

Example - 


public class Person {
  private String name; // private = restricted access

  // Getter
  public String getName() {
    return name;
  }

  // Setter
  public void setName(String newName) {
    this.name = newName;
  }
}
